  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the safety and efficacy of the Endograb system
      which is an internal laparoscopic retractor device. This retractor device is inserted into
      the abdominal cavity through one of the 5 mm trocars and obviates the need for a separate
      dedicated trocar for retraction. Therefore enables the reduction of the number of abdominal
      incisions in a laparoscopic operation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
